===Pronunciation===
אדמה / 'ădâmâh / ad-aw-maw'

===Etymology===
From {{HH|119}}; 

===Noun===
'''אדמה'''

# Soil (from its general redness): - country, earth, ground, husband [-man] (-ry), land.

